Come on.

153
00:13:03,125 --> 00:13:04,685
Yah, yah!

154
00:13:08,165 --> 00:13:11,965
- [galloping]
- [grunting]

155
00:13:13,445 --> 00:13:14,965
- [man shouts]
- [horse whinnies]

156
00:13:16,445 --> 00:13:18,965
[groans]

157
00:13:20,925 --> 00:13:22,325
You're either on my side...

158
00:13:24,445 --> 00:13:26,205
