- [thwack]
<i>- </i>[Rasputin groans]

160
00:13:28,725 --> 00:13:32,165
[Smith] Rasputin is one of the most
remarkable figures of the 20th century.

161
00:13:32,245 --> 00:13:34,325
Okay, we can talk.

162
